34
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,625
Congratulations!

35
00:04:28,626 --> 00:04:35,792
By the way, did you know that the /ʊ/ sound is most frequently written as the letter 'u'?

36
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:45,540
The /ʊ/ sound is represented by the letter 'u,' as in the word "put," in 45% of cases.

37
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:52,920
Almost the same percentage of words with this sound is written as the combination of the letters 'oo,'

38
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:55,163
as in the word "book."

39
00:04:55,800 --> 00:05:01,480
The remaining 10% are split between the letter 'o,' as in the word "wolf,"

40
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:07,600
and the combination of the letters 'ou,' as in the word "could."

